<p class="by-author-img"><img alt='荒濱　 一' src='http://cybozushiki.cybozu.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/hajime-arahama_avatar-40x40.jpg' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></p>  
            
<div class="entry-metaList">
<p class="by-author"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://cybozushiki.cybozu.co.jp/?author=23" title="荒濱　 一 の投稿をすべて表示" rel="author">荒濱　 一</a></span></p>
